::Feline::

She looked at Zardus with a smile.  She leaned close to him and 
whispered,"So handsome, could I practice my...charm on you sometime?" 
She softly purred into his ear and straightened up.  She walked next 
to him, swing her hips and swishing her tail. And purring ever so 
softly.
